classitems.description:
Save a statement, when used from a browser sends to the endpoint using the RESTful interface.
Use a callback to make the call asynchronous.
classitems.name: saveStatement

classitems.description: Retrieve a statement, when used from a browser sends to the endpoint using the RESTful interface.
classitems.name: retrieveStatement

Use a callback to make the call asynchronous.

classitems.description:
Fetch a set of statements, when used from a browser sends to the endpoint using the
RESTful interface.  Use a callback to make the call asynchronous.
classitems.name: queryStatements

props.name: since
props.description: Match statements stored since specified timestamp

props.name: until
props.description: Match statements stored at or before specified timestamp

props.name: attachments
props.description: Include attachments in multipart response or don't (defualt: false)

props.name: ascending
props.description: Return results in ascending order of stored time

props.name: target
props.description: (Removed in 1.0.0, use 'activity' or 'agent' instead) Activity, Agent, or Statement matches 'object'

props.name: context
props.description: (Removed in 1.0.0, use 'activity' instead) When filtering on target, include statements with matching context

props.name: sparse
props.description: (Removed in 1.0.0, use 'format' instead) Get sparse results

props.name: err
props.description: Error status or null if succcess
